# Management as Code (MaC) Protocol

At the very beginning of every session/conversation in this repository, you MUST ALWAYS READ the `MaC/ritual_de_sesion.md` file FIRST before executing any other prompts.

1. Do NOT write any code, execute any scripts, or make any changes before reading `MaC/ritual_de_sesion.md`.
2. Strictly follow the "Modos de Operación" and the "Ritual de Inicio de Sesión" described in `ritual_de_sesion.md`.
3. Plan and execute your tasks within `MaC/sesiones/sesion-*.md` as instructed.
